---

## cp

Copies files.

```bash
cp notes.txt backup.txt
```

---

## mv

Moves or renames files.

```bash
mv linux.txt linux-basics.txt
```

---

## rm

Deletes files.

```bash
rm backup.txt
```

---

## find

Searches files.

```bash
find . -name "*.txt"
```

---

## man

Displays command manual.

```bash
man ls
```

